# Experiment run artefacts (traces, ratings, index) — can grow large
# and are maintainer-local. The harness CODE (runner.py, pipeline.py,
# steps/, variants/, rate.py, seeds.py) remains tracked; only the
# SETUP fixtures and RESULTS are gitignored.
.ai/

# The published experiment surface is the generic harness only
# (runner.py, pipeline.py, rate.py, rate_variant.py, seeds.py,
# preflight_db_retrieve.py, __init__.py). The actual experiments —
# variant pipelines, per-variant step implementations, test fixtures,
# rubric, and the maintainer's narrative — are maintainer-local.
experiments/variants/
experiments/steps/
experiments/prompts/
experiments/rubric.yaml
experiments/LOG.md

